                    Users must use the application for personal productivity purposes only and should not attempt
                    to misuse or manipulate the software in ways that could harm the application or other users.
                </Text>

                <Label text="2. Data Handling" styleClass="subsection-label" />
                <Text wrappingWidth="660" textAlignment="JUSTIFY" styleClass="description-text">
                    Verve Planner stores user data locally on your device. We do not share, sell, or transmit
                    your personal data to third parties.
                </Text>

                <Label text="3. Liability" styleClass="subsection-label" />
                <Text wrappingWidth="660" textAlignment="JUSTIFY" styleClass="description-text">
                    Verve Planner is provided as-is. We are not responsible for any data loss or device issues
                    that may occur while using the application.
                </Text>

                <Label text="4. Updates to Terms" styleClass="subsection-label" />
                <Text wrappingWidth="660" textAlignment="JUSTIFY" styleClass="description-text">
                    We may update these Terms and Conditions occasionally. Updated terms will be reflected within
                    the app, and continued use indicates acceptance.
                </Text>

                <Label text="5. Contact Us" styleClass="subsection-label" />
                <Text wrappingWidth="660" textAlignment="JUSTIFY" styleClass="description-text">
                    If you have any questions about these terms, please contact us at: info@vplanner.com
                </Text>
            </VBox>
        </ScrollPane>

        <HBox alignment="CENTER" styleClass="footer">
            <Label text="© 2025 Verve Planner — All Rights Reserved." />
        </HBox>

    </VBox>

</AnchorPane>
